title: 28,000 Guitar Pro Tab Files
description:
28,000 Guitar Tabliture Files for Guitar Pro. Minimum version supported is 3.0.1. If you need Guitar Pro you can find it rather easily but it is not included with this file, these are only tab files.

Guitar Pro is required to use these files, they cannot be read as raw text.


Have fun!
